headline: Protests Shake Nicolás Maduro's Government
author: NA
content: Miles take to the streets due to shortages of chicken, milk, flour, and toilet paper. There are dozens of injured and detained students.

headline: Padre defiende a su hijo acusado de abandono
author: NA
content: Pavón: My son is not abandoned.

headline: Sicarios en moto matan a dos y lanzan 'calzoncillos Guty'
author: NA
content: Moto-riding hitmen kill two and throw 'Guty's underwear.'
